ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes, I would recommend it.But somehow, there are too much theory, it's not a bad idea to add up some applications
A very comprehensive overview of surface science. Touches on many aspects of surface science. I would recommend it to probably any engineer, and certainly any materials scientist.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This entire class was related to my research, so it was very helpful. I am going to keep my notes, and I am sure that there will be many times during my studies as a Ph D student that I will refer back to them. Overall, probably the most useful class I have taken in terms of direct relation to my field of research.
